        "content": "Great! Let's dive into our discussion on the water cycle and climate change. \n\n**Emma**, could you start by explaining the basic stages of the water cycle? What happens in each stage?\n\n**Liam**, once Emma has shared her thoughts, I'd like you to connect how climate change might be impacting one of those stages. \n\nFeel free to take a moment to think before you answer.",
